description: Dan Udoh's opener and a calamitous own goal from Jack Armer hand high-flying Wycombe victory.
title: Wycombe Wanderers 2-0 Burton Albion
title_page: Wycombe Wanderers 2-0 Burton Albion - BBC Sport
maintext:
Wycombe have only lost one of their last eight league meetings with Burton Albion (W5 D2), a 1-2 defeat in March 2023.
Burton Albion have lost four of their last five league visits to Wycombe Wanderers (although drew the most recent 0-0 in August 2023) since a 3-1 win in November 2014.
Wycombe have lost just one of their last 15 home league games (W9 D5), a 0-1 defeat to Huddersfield in January.
